You are working on an Amazon FBA arbitrage automation system with a FastAPI dashboard. The dashboard runs at `localhost:8001` via `uvicorn dashboard_v2_redesign.api:app --reload --port 8001`.

**The main active work** is `dashboard_v2_redesign/` — a new dashboard UI replacing the legacy streamlit dashboard.

