**LLM routing**: Chat UI uses kimi (`CONTROL_PLANE_LLM_PROVIDER=kimi`). Analyst subprocess uses opencode (`ANALYST_LLM_PROVIDER=opencode` set in `api.py::run_job()`). These are intentionally independent.

**Known open issue**: Log lineage may still show sandbox logs for main workflow. Added `print(f"[LOG-LINEAGE-FIX] Error: ...")` to diagnose. Check uvicorn output.

